  cognitive-frameworks own#1 (doc-english-required, deps)
  cognitive-frameworks own#14 (readme-sealed-required, deps)
  cognitive-frameworks own#35 (hive-resource-only-mandate, grandfathered)
  cognitive-frameworks raw#33 (ai-native-english-only, mk1 promotion)
  enforce hexa ~/core/hexa-lang/tool/readme_english_audit.hexa
